{"tid":1326574,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【換機最大原因】新 iPhone 有望採用經典彩虹蘋果標誌","createTime":"2019-07-17T09:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T19:10:30.000Z","uid":109923,"like":8,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6bed96e9767809a9ef1cc3996da273a09b48512c","tid":1326574,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"【換GAY最大原因】新 iPhone 有望採用經典彩虹蘋果標誌<br />\n<br />\n咬了一口的 Apple 品牌標誌，相信大家對它絕不陌生，不過六色彩虹蘋果標誌，自從近年改用單色蘋果標誌後，已經成為經典。最近有傳 Apple 打算在部分新產品上重新應用這個六色彩虹蘋果標誌，不知能否成為大家換機的主要原因呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcqYaht.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcqYaht.png&h=8868a246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然消息來源未有指出什麼新產品會應用經典彩虹蘋果標誌，但已做出多張電腦加工圖，換上彩虹蘋果標誌的 iPhone 及 Macbook Pro，蘋果標誌位置比單色變得更為奪目，有助提升辨別率。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：macrumors"},{"pid":"d27b0adedef891983738f97f83530bfb648aa485","tid":1326574,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"彩虹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6d3f29f6b05153b443830fa7cbbf939374e532","tid":1326574,"uid":57674,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"唔好啦屌<br />\n利申：非恐同，純粹覺得好柒"},{"pid":"2318361cad003482f130f618f5db299642aa4bf0","tid":1326574,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"又係果D乜撚野LGBT"},{"pid":"ee6edc7709ac84fcb95a6e103a56360676bf393e","tid":1326574,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b984bea3448013ee1068f257ea20642d44c090f","tid":1326574,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"彩虹=同性戀？"},{"pi